00:15:31.500 --> 00:15:33.130
Oh, Hikaru!

00:15:35.840 --> 00:15:36.630
Hikaru!

00:15:37.670 --> 00:15:40.870
Huh? Dia adalah istrinya paman itu?

00:15:45.050 --> 00:15:47.380
